</p>
<h2 id="building-the-query">Building the Query <a class="headerlink" href="query-builder#building-the-query" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Now, let's chain some awesomeness! The <code>QueryBuilder</code> has methods on it like
<code>andWhere</code>, <code>leftJoin</code> and <code>addOrderBy</code>. Let's use that - pass <code>cat.name</code>
as the first argument and <code>DESC</code> as the second:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="115057cbed">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
                        <span class="js-expand-all" data-range="1-25" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Show All Lines" data-placement="top">
