	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-3001953342" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>Yes! Then `gory` will be an alias of that table, in which entity repository you call this "createQueryBuilder('gory')" method, i.e. if you call "$this-&gt;createQueryBuilder('gory')" inside the CategoryRepository, then `gory` will be an alias of category table ;)</p><p>Cheers!</p>
	                            </div>
